Description: Aptura COSMIC desktop integration
 Installs Aptura's COSMIC integration, desktop launchers, and utility hooks.
 The default desktop uses System76 COSMIC with Aptura retro-COSMIC branding,
 practical workstation tools, firmware visibility, power controls, and a local
 system health check.
